Yes, you will see improvement without the upgraded backbone. You just won't realize the full potential without it. The issue is many consumers do not understand the fine print and they see BIG NUMBERS on the box, but miss the small print that says they need the better backbone to see full potential. Creates mismatched expectations for many.

